Source: https://github.com/valdisiljuconoks/localization-provider-core
Title: Localization Provider for .Net Core applications
Description: Alternative localization provider based on EF. You will forget about clumsy Resx files and will be able to work with translations in strongly-typed manner. No more magic strings.
Website: https://github.com/valdisiljuconoks/localization-provider-core/blob/master/README.md
Docs: https://github.com/valdisiljuconoks/localization-provider-core/blob/master/README.md
Language: C#
